<p>By integrating Oracle services, Polygon aims to achieve real-time data feeds and secure off-chain computation, enabling dynamic scalability adjustments based on actual network demand. </p>



<p>This integration allows Polygon to access external data in a secure and decentralized manner, providing accurate and timely information for optimizing scalability parameters.</p>



