<li><strong>Optimized Resource Allocation</strong>: By adjusting block sizes based on demand, resources are allocated optimally, preventing congestion and maintaining fast transaction speeds.</li>



<li><strong>Future-Proofing</strong>: As user activity and network growth continue to evolve, the dynamic block size ensures that the network can adapt and scale accordingly, future-proofing the ecosystem.</li>
</ul>



<p>With the dynamic block size mechanism in place, Polygon can effectively address the ever-changing demands of its user base while ensuring a seamless and reliable experience for all participants.</p>



